723367f-a.title: Manhattan: Spring Street - Wooster Street
723367f-a.text:
Spring Street, north side, from Wooster Street to, but not in-
cluding, West Broadway (formerly South Fifth Avenue). Na. 143
Spring Street is the frame house on the N.W. corner of Wooster
Street. No. 147, the loft building between thc two taller ones,
is an example of brick building faced with iron.
1932.
J. Clarence Davies Collection, Museum of the City of New York.
Negative No. 557.
CREDIT LINE IMPRRATIVE ON ALL REPRODUCTIONS.
